<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p>感谢以下各位为本文提出的意见<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/2big" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150188); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6150188&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222221" alt="2BIG" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6150188)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/2big" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150188); return false;">2BIG</a></span><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222221" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
<p>本文与由Kalafina所演唱的《空之境界：忘却录音》的主题曲<a href="https://music.163.com/#/song?id=34229164">Fairtytale</a>以及杉浦勇纪所创作的<a href="https://www.xiami.com/song/1772535659?spm=a1z1s.6659513.0.0.0HXFrM">镜花水月</a>搭配食用可能会更佳</p>
<p>本文可能会扩写成一篇异常项目，看合著者<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fengyi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4750546); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4750546&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222221" alt="Dr FengYi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4750546)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fengyi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4750546); return false;">Dr FengYi</a></span>怎么写</p>
<p>这是我对酩酊街的一点理解，只有被遗忘的酩酊之人才能进入那条时间停滞的街道。</p>
<p>另外介绍了一下SCP-CN-1930之后的故事，那个被救下的孩子是我的下层叙事投影，酩酊街不可能不知道萤火虫们死了的这件事，这也算是酩酊街的一个回复吧。</p>
<p>另外感谢Wuddy<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wuddy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4388084); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4388084&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222221" alt="Wuddy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4388084)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wuddy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4388084); return false;">Wuddy</a></span>在本文中出演。</p>
